comments: McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact to Sexton's (CLE) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Sexton (CLE) reaches in and makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) arm.
Mobley (CLE) avoids making contact to Lillard's (POR) arm, and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) briefly places two hands on Rubio (CLE) and he makes marginal contact that does not affect his SQBR.
Lillard (POR) makes contact with the ball and he dislodges it from Sexton (CLE).
Following the pass, Garland (CLE) moves into Simons' (POR) path and he initiates foot to contact with Simons that affects his SQBR in transition.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Lillard (POR) throws an errant pass OOB.
McCollum (POR) avoids making contact to Sexton's (CLE) arm, and he cleanly dislodges the ball during the driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the OOB called on McCollum (POR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful and CLE maintains possession of the ball.
Rubio (CLE) does not inbound the ball within the five seconds allotted to his team.
Sexton (CLE) does not make contact with Lillard's (POR) arm. However, Mobley (CLE) swipes down and makes contact to Lillard's arm during his driving shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) stops and Osman's (CLE) momentum carries him into Lillard's body but the contact is marginal.
Nurkic (POR) dislodges Osman (CLE) from his position during the rebound.
